My first time in and it was just what I was looking for. It's a rainy day, so I jumped at the black bean chili. Richly flavored and chock full of beans and veggies that still had a nice crunch. My fresh veggie wrap was absolutely delicious. The hummus melded with the dill marinade into a yummy sauce for the crisp vegetables wrapped in a hearty spinach wrap. My tummy is very happy. Friendly, cheerful staff as well. This will certainly be one of regular spots.

